subject: Track and Field
lead_paragraph: The Brazilian sprinter Luciano Pagliarini won the fourth stage of the Tour of Missouri, and George Hincapie retained the overall lead. Pagliarini, racing for the Spanish team Saunier Duval-Prodir, finished the 133-mile stage in 5 hours 7 minutes 52 seconds.
